label: Component
description: A ISO:PhysicalObject that  may have some OMPD:ResourceRole

label: Hazard
description: An ISO: Realizeable Entity that is realizrd in some OMPD: Hazard Realization Process

label: HazardInMaintenanceProcess
description: An OMPD: Hazard that is realized in some OMPD: Hazard Realization Process that occurs relative to some OMPD: Maintenance Process

label: HazardRealizationProcess
description: An ISO: Activity that has the potential to cause harm

label: MaintainableItem
description: An ISO:PhysicalObject hat has a role OMPD:MaintainableItemRole

label: MaintainableItemRole
description: An ISO:Role that is the role of the item that work is performed on in a OMPD:MaintenanceProcess

label: MaintenanceProcedureDocument
description: An ISO:InformationObject that is about some OMPD:MaineanceProcedureProcess

label: MaintenanceProcedureProcess
description: An OMPD:MaintenanceProcess that is represented in some OMPD:MaintenanceProcedureDocument and has activity part some OMPD:MaintenanceTask

label: MaintenanceProcess
description: An ISO: Activity, intended to repair or restore an item to a state in which it can perform its required function

label: MaintenanceTask
description: An OMPD:MaintenanceProcess that is: - a direct activity part of zero or one OMPD:MaintenanceProcedureProcess - an activity part of zero or more OMPD:MaintenanceProcedureProcess - a direct activity part of zero or one OMPD:MaintenanceTask - an activity part of zero or more OMPD:MaintenanceTask - occurs directly before zero or one Maintenance task - occurs before zero or more MaintenanceTask - occurs directly after zero or one MaintenanceTask - occurs after zero or more OMPD:MaintenanceTask

label: MaintenanceTaskDescription
description: An ISO:InformationObject that is about some OMPD:MaintenanceTask

label: Material
description: A ISO:PhysicalObject that may have some OMPD:ResourceRole

label: Permit
description: A ISO:InformationObject that  may have some OMPD:ResourceRole

label: Qualification
description: A ISO:Quality that is beared by zero or more OMPD:QualitifiedPerson

label: QualifiedPerson
description: A ISO:Person that may have some OMPD:ResourceRole and has a OMPD:Qualification

label: Resource
description: An ISO: Object that has some OMPD: Resource Role

label: ResourceRole
description: An ISO:Role that is the role of an ISO:Object that is required to execute some ISO:Activity

label: Tool
description: A ISO:PhysicalObject that  may have some OMPD:ResourceRole
